                   midgard.admin.acl Changelog
                   ---------------------------
Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completly new features.

2006-05-26 bergie
  + Added support for displaying all assignees that have privileges
  + Added the Magic Assignees to the list
  + Added support for component-specific privileges

2006-05-10 bergie
  + Switched to the full () Allow () Deny () Inherit ACL system
  - Added localizations

2006-05-08 bergie
  + Initial simple implementation enabling setting of ALLOW privileges
